title: Jo Kwon puts on makeup for 'Allure' | allkpop.com
text:
Or Login / Register With Us Forgot Password? Remember Me Jo Kwon puts on makeup for 'Allure' By jennywill 4 minutes ago 1,226 68 0 0 Google+ Jo Kwon got together with ' Allure ' for a one-of-a-kind photoshoot!
Jo Kwon has been doing a lot of cross dressing and heavy makeup lately especially for ' Golden Tambourine ', and he showed his artistry once again for the magazine. The magazine explained they chose him instantly for a photoshoot that involved makeup and a male model.
